Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_oa_design_cell(25.10)                          init_oa_design_cell(25.10)

Name
       init_oa_design_cell

Syntax
        init_oa_design_cell <cellname>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies the OpenAccess design cell name to be used. It is used by the
       init_design command.

       This  global variable replaces the previous rda_Input(ui_oa_designCell)
       configuration file variable.

Example
              * The following command specifies  myOACell  as  the  OpenAccess
                database cell.

                set init_oa_design_cell {myOACell}

Related Information
              * init_design

